               <p>AND THREE OTHER COUNTS - for uttering and publishing as true a like forged acceptance, with the same intention.</p>
               <p>The case was stated by Mr. Knapp.</p>
               <p>ABRAHAM WILDEY ROBARTS Q. What is the firm of your house - A. 
               <persName id="t18111030-44-person394">
                  Abraham 
                  Robarts
               <interp inst="t18111030-44-person394" type="surname" value="Robarts"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111030-44-person394" type="given" value="Abraham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111030-44-person394" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , Sir 
               <persName id="t18111030-44-person395">
                  William 
                  Curtis
               <interp inst="t18111030-44-person395" type="surname" value="Curtis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111030-44-person395" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111030-44-person395" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , Bart. 
               <persName id="t18111030-44-person396">
                  Abraham 
                  Wildey
               <interp inst="t18111030-44-person396" type="surname" value="Wildey"></interp>
