            . - A. I am, his stables are in King Street, Westminster.</p>
               <p>Q. You know your brother's hand writing. - A. Very well, I have seen him write very often.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at that acceptance, and say whether that is his hand writing. - A. No ways like it, it is not his writing.</p>
               <p>Mr. Alley. You are come here to tell us that it is no ways like it, are you his partner. - A. No, we are not concerned in trade.</p>
               <p>Q You both carry on the same business. - A. Yes, we are no ways connected in business.</p>
               <p>Court. Do you know any other person of the name of 
               <persName id="t18111030-44-person409">
                  Thomas 
