               <p>Q. Look at that and tell me according to your belief whether that is his hand writing or not. - A. No, it is not.</p>
               <p>Mr. Alley. Do you form your opinion solely upon the hand writing, supposing you had seen it elsewhere. - A. I should be able to have said it was not his handwriting.</p>
